              ul.text-gray-700.space-y-1
                li • Dynamic signal routing
                li • Pattern recognition
                li • Automated responses
                li • Conditional processing
                li • Event-driven handling
                li • User-defined logic

            .bg-gray-50.rounded-lg.p-4
              h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-2 Processing Rules
              ul.text-gray-700.space-y-1
                li • Signal routing rules
                li • Protocol conversion
                li • Quality thresholds
                li • Performance optimization
                li • Error handling
                li • Recovery procedures

          h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Signal Quality Monitoring

          p.text-gray-700.mb-4
            | Monitor signal quality, performance, and system health in real-time.

          .grid.md:grid-cols-2.gap-6.mb-8
            .bg-gray-50.rounded-lg.p-4
