          h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Advanced Features

          h3.text-2xl.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 Signal Processing
          p.text-gray-700.mb-4
            | Advanced signal processing capabilities for complex applications.

          ul.list-disc.list-inside.text-gray-700.space-y-2.mb-6
            li Digital signal processing (DSP) algorithms
            li Multi-protocol signal conversion
            li Adaptive signal routing
            li Pattern recognition and analysis
            li Signal conditioning and filtering
            li Performance optimization

          h3.text-2xl.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 Interactive Control
          p.text-gray-700.mb-4
            | Interactive control features for dynamic signal management.

          ul.list-disc.list-inside.text-gray-700.space-y-2.mb-6
            li Real-time signal routing changes
