          h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Alerting & Notifications

          p.text-gray-700.mb-4
            | Configure comprehensive alerting and notification systems for signal monitoring.

          .grid.md:grid-cols-2.gap-6.mb-8
            .bg-gray-50.rounded-lg.p-4
