          h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Troubleshooting

          .bg-red-50.border-l-4.border-red-400.p-4.mb-6
            h3.text-lg.font-semibold.text-red-900.mb-2 Common Issues
            ul.text-red-800.space-y-1
              li • Web interface not loading - check network connection
              li • Signal routing not working - verify channel configuration
              li • Poor signal quality - check connections and grounding
              li • High latency - optimize signal processing settings
              li • Network connectivity issues - check IP configuration
              li • Signal conversion errors - verify protocol settings

          h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Best Practices

          .bg-green-50.border-l-4.border-green-400.p-4.mb-6
            h3.text-lg.font-semibold.text-green-900.mb-2 Signal Control Tips
            ul.text-green-800.space-y-1
              li • Plan your signal routing topology before configuration
              li • Test signal quality and timing for each connection
              li • Set up redundant signal paths for critical applications
              li • Monitor signal quality and performance regularly
              li • Keep firmware updated for best performance
              li • Document your signal routing configuration

          h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Support and Resources

          p.text-gray-700.mb-6
            | For additional help with the web interface, check our resources or contact support.

          .flex.flex-col.sm:flex-row.gap-4
